name: "Portofino" Limited Edition Canvas Print
description:

Every print is signed, numbered, and titled by Lori Gilbert 

Each print measures 22" x 28" inches and .75" in depth and is printed on PureWhite™ canvas is specially developed for HP Latex printing technology. These are truly individual works of art. All prints are handled with archival care throughout printing, signing, handling, and shipping phases.
